Barbara Castleton https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Barbara_Castleton 0 Barbara Castleton (September 14, 1894 – December 23, 1978) was an American silent film actress. Castleton appeared in motion pictures from 1914 through 1923, accumulating twenty-eight screen credits.
